window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Your favorite dragon is back, and he's richer than ever!</b></p> <p>Months have passed since Vainqueur Knightsbane, great calamity of his age and best dragon in the world, discovered the class system and adventurer lifestyle. More powerful than he has ever been, the great wyrm faces a new challenge: administering the lands he conquered.&nbsp;</p> <p>At his side, his long-suffering minion Victor Dalton struggles to maintain peace in a country where taxes are illegal, angels sell insurance, and demons are the lawyers. Old enemies plot their revenge, and thieves slither in the dark.</p> <p>Vainqueur better keep his vault locked at night!</p>"; 
